      <h1 class='title'>Dounreay (Decommissioning)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c244WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_244ws' title='Col. 244WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c244WS' name='column_244ws' href='#column_244ws' rel='bookmark'>244WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06135'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_173'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-vincent-cable' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_173' title='Link to this speech by Dr Vincent Cable' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-vincent-cable" title="Dr Vincent Cable">Dr. Cable</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06135">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what implications costs arising from the decommissioning of Dounreay have for the estimated cost of decommissioning other publicly held nuclear liabilities; and if she will make a statement. [88051]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06136'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_174'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-brian-wilson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_174' title='Link to this speech by Mr Brian Wilson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-brian-wilson" title="Mr Brian Wilson">Mr. Wilson</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06136"> <span class="italic">[holding answer 19 December 2002]:</span> The programme for decommissioning nuclear licensed sites is a matter for the nuclear site license holders and their regulators, taking into account Government policy on nuclear decommissioning. The programme at Dounreay has no special implications for the cost of dealing with other publicly held nuclear liabilities.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
